strings:
<voice_0x010011C9><se_def>David: Here you are, Leopold! Dinner time!
I'll leave it here for you.
<voice_0x010011CB><se_def>David: I-I'm sorry! H-Have I done something to upset you? Please... I'm truly sorry!
<voice_0x010011CD><se_def>David: Thanks for what you did before! It's because of you that Master Dominico is safe.
<voice_0x010011CE><se_def>David: ...Are you on your travels, by any chance?

<voice_0x010011CF><se_def>David: I thought so! I could tell.
I was travelling around the world myself
until about six months ago.
<voice_0x010011D0><se_def>David: But I can tell you are by the way you're dressed. I was travelling around the world myself until about six months ago.
<voice_0x010011D1><se_def>David: Yeah, it'd be six months ago now. When I got here I was penniless and so hungry I collapsed.
<voice_0x010011D3><se_def>David: He said he'd let me work for him here at his house. I was so grateful.

<voice_0x010011D4><se_def>David: He can be a bit overbearing at times.
But in his heart, he's a truly kind man.
